<h2><%= @order.address.first_name %>, bring a friend to Theater Wit for free</h2>

<p>
  Thanks for being a member. I want to extend an invitation to bring a friend for free the next time
  you come by. So, here's a one-use discount code for <b>a free admission</b> to one of our productions.
</p><p>
  To use it, you'll need to make two reservations (our software doesn't allow us to combine membership reservations
  with other offers yet). After you make your member reservation, make a second one for a general admission
  ticket using the special offer code <b><%= @special_offer.code %></b>.  Your code is good for six months so
  no rush!
</p>
<p>
  As part of your membership, you'll get one of the these passes every six months as a thank you. For more information
  about supporting Theater Wit, you can read <a href="http://www.theaterwit.org/join/index.php">this</a>
  or give me a call at 773-975-8150.
</p><p>
  See you at the theater!<br/>
  <%= image_tag "http://www.theaterwit.org/static/img/mail/jmwsignature.png" -%><br clear="all"/>
  Jeremy Wechsler<br/>
  Artistic Director,<br/>
  Theater Wit</br>
</p>
